capture-vat-application-number.line_2                         = The VAT application number was displayed on the screen after an application for VAT registration was made. It was also emailed and will be on the VAT registration letter we sent in the post.
capture-vat-application-number.hint                           = It is 12 numbers and begins with ‘099’, for example 099 123456789.
